Class Command

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.safs.model.AbstractTestRecord
      • org.safs.model.AbstractCommand
        • org.safs.model.Command
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TestRecordParametersInterface
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BlockID, Breakpoint, DriverCommand, EngineCommand, ProjectCommand, Skipped

    public class Command
extends AbstractCommand
    An extra layer to differentiate between ComponentFunction commands and all other types of commands. All commands except ComponentFunction commands will subclass from this Command class. ComponentFunction commands subclass AbstractCommand directly.
